?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zyHCJYBYP3oQ7kNvgHwn2Tq&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDd3d2Wg4CgCv7P37IBXs8lwZWNtuoc-jLz3p77e8xtNw&oe=66E2E177"}, "display_name": "Level scary!", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# Level Scary: A Gorilla Tag Fan Game\n\n**Level Scary** is an immersive VR horror game inspired by the popular **Gorilla Tag**. Currently in **beta**, this fan game takes the familiar mechanics of Gorilla Tag and adds a terrifying twist.\n\n## Features\n\n- **Playable Model**: Experience the game with a detailed and responsive play model.\n- **Working Mods**: Enhance your gameplay with various mods that introduce new elements of fear.\n- **Vent System**: Navigate through a network of vents, adding to the suspenseful atmosphere.\n- **Multiplayer Servers**: Join friends or face the horror alone in a thrilling multiplayer setting.\n\n## Gameplay\n\nPlayers navigate through dark, eerie environments filled with unexpected scares and challenging obstacles. The game features a detailed play model, working mods, and a network of vents that add to the suspenseful atmosphere.\n\n## Beta Phase\n\nAs **Level Scary** is currently in beta, players can experience the core gameplay while providing valuable feedback for future improvements.\n\n---\n\nDive into **Level Scary** and test your nerves in this spine-chilling VR experience that pushes the boundaries of traditional Gorilla Tag gameplay.\n{469350875616633}", "short_description": "\"Level Scary\" is a beta VR horror game inspired by Gorilla Tag. This fan game features a playable model, functional mods, vents, and servers for a thrilling multiplayer experience."}]}, "developer_name": "Aden Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://prutuo.github.io/AdenPrivacyPolicy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Aden Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://levelscary.github.io/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_